room_title: Escape room "Revenge on the Bayou" by Clue Carré in New Orleans
room_address: 830 Union Street Suite 101 New Orleans, LA 70112
room_description: The tales of Julie White, an evil voodoo priestess, have swirled through the Manchac Swamp like the storms that have plagued the area since her death. While there are those who believe there’s more to Julie’s story than meets the eye, those that sought to explore her cabin have either turned back in fear or disappeared into the swamp. Now, you have stumbled upon her dwelling as a storm builds on the horizon. Can you solve the mystery of Julie White and bring peace to the swamp before being swept away in a torrent of wind and water?
